refsection.programlisting:
Probability estimates (need '-b 1' for training and testing):

     [label_vector, instance_vector] = readsparse('heart_scale');
     model = svmtrain(label_vector, instance_vector, '-c 1 -g 0.07 -b 1');
     [label_vector, instance_vector] = readsparse('heart_scale');
     [predict_label, accuracy, prob_estimates] = svmpredict(label_vector, instance_vector, model, '-b 1');
